It can have value from selection list "CSA-Property-ValueType". This Input is required only when Input "onlyUpdate" is selected as "no". values - One or more values dilimited by comma , (If user want to use some other separator for multiple values then needs to be pass as next input "separator") separator - A delimiter that separates elements in the values ( default dilimiter used is comma ,) b8f19bae-c03b-459f-9994-7877f53cfc46.699d93bc-b924-4ef9-a86f-44d1ba7ce5ee.prompt=Service Component Id b8f19bae-c03b-459f-9994-7877f53cfc46.7bf2d27a-1e87-4c8f-bbd5-b42a576e5193.prompt=Artifact ID b8f19bae-c03b-459f-9994-7877f53cfc46.8e0922b2-6d36-42a5-a7df-4b1fec989879.prompt=Enter a value for value1 b8f19bae-c03b-459f-9994-7877f53cfc46.a3e7ce84-3591-4bd9-a43c-6770b197fa6d.prompt=Service Instance Id b8f19bae-c03b-459f-9994-7877f53cfc46.af136ce7-cae5-4a58-a5c9-bde210d7f86d.description=This workflow returns the artifact's properties and values using Artifact APIs. result\: propertyNameValuesList\: pipe separated list of property name and values ( where each property name and values would be ; seprated and multiple values would be , seprated) e.g. - property 1; value1,value2|property 2; value3|property 3; value3,value4|........ b8f19bae-c03b-459f-9994-7877f53cfc46.bcb3148f-5e0b-4e51-a24a-169d90dea0c1.description=
Adds two numbers together

Inputs\:
value1 - The first value.
value2 - The second value.

Returns\:
The sum of the two numbers.

Responses\:
success - The operation completed successfully.
failure - Something went wrong.
